x._AHFinderDirect_ is implemented as a\nthorn in the_Cactus_ computational toolkit, and is freely available by\nanonymous CVS checkout.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jun 2003 21:47:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Jul 2003 20:15:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 27 Oct 2003 11:01:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
